data.description: Welcome to Sandy Creek Ranch, a lovely property nestled in the heart of Livingston, TX with 17 acres, providing ample space for your equestrian pursuits with barn/stables. Appreciate there are five stalls, an air conditioned tack/storage room, a wash rack, and grooming areas, it's designed to cater to the needs of both horse and owner. The riding arena conveys with the right offer. A pasture boasts a pond and animal shelters. Relax and unwind in the outdoor spaces designed for leisure.     The barndo is still a blank slate to customize to your liking. There is a 20x8 workroom adjacent to the barndo. The fridges convey. A covered patio or deck provides the ideal spot for enjoying your morning coffee or entertaining guests while taking in the picturesque surroundings.    Conveniently situated in Livingston, you'll find the perfect balance of rural tranquility and accessibility to local amenities. Explore nearby trails, parks, and lakes, offering a variety of recreational opportunities.
